Package playn.core

Class Json.TypedArray.Util

  • java.lang.Object
    • playn.core.Json.TypedArray.Util
  • Enclosing interface:
    Json.TypedArray<T>

    public static class Json.TypedArray.Util
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains utility methods for creating typed arrays to supply as the default when fetching optional typed arrays from your JSON model. For example: 
    
 Json.TypedArray<Integer> sizes = json.getArray(
   "sizes", Integer.class, Json.TypedArray.Util.create(3, 5, 9));
